
Test Cases & boundary:

1) i)input list for recyclerView shold not be empty -- populate the list.
  ii)in case empty list show empty text message and recyclerView visibility is set to gone.
2) i)item click of recyclerview should not have null url value to intent data
 ii) if on item click url is null then it will not intent to next activity to play video.
3) i) videoUrl should not be null while setting the uri in videoView
  ii) in case videoUrl is null showing error message alert --and on dismiss of alert dialog return to the previous activity.
4) i)showing progressBar when data is buffering and
 ii)while playing progressBar should not be visible.
5)Internet permission should be declaredin manifest file.